            <![CDATA[
                    <img src="https://www.virtualhouse.ml/media/posts/2/room-01.png" alt="" />
                <p>Welcome home! The room has 4 places for people seated by the table. It is furnished by furniture usable in living rooms, bed rooms and other individual rooms where people stay to spend time, for example with their friends by a cup of coffee. You may like to rezz it at any place where you want to have a nice chat with your partner(s). <br><br>The items you can get here include some wider picture frames. In the room they have pictures in them I made, but you can replace those. After you rezz your house again, the originals will appear. <br><br>The chairs are covered by the textile which can be used separatedly. It contains a lot of useful anims. You can use these objects to animate your own furniture. 2 people can lay or cuddle on the bed and there are some other useful objects in the room, you can just take.</p>
<p class="msg msg--info">Fully rezzed the scene occupies 83 prims, house included<br> and it is 9.6 x 0.8 m2 large.</p>
